<br>
Unfortunately, this is an open raid.  This means a couple things.<br>
<br>
1)  It's a training raid.  A lot of people here have never raided before.  So they don't behave in a good manner.<br>
2) This behavoir results in a lot of spam in raid channels.<br>
3) Spam prevents reading as it scrolls off to fast.<br>
4) People have preconceived notions of how loot will go.  They don't bother reading what was said or check their logfiles, they just come here to rant.<br>
5) Rasza has not been 65 very long.  I know Rasza would do any legitimate means to defend his guilds honor.  /d is one of those.  Too bad your spineless/gimp.<br>
<br>
The part that is the most humorous.  Your talking about a Runed Bolster Belt.  This is a tradable loot item of moderate value.  <br>
<br>
Why the emotional attachment to this item?<br>
It's not an epic (or other large quest) drop?<br>
It's only worth the pp to someone who wins the roll?<br>
It's got a lot of classes on it, surely you don't think you'd have won?<br>
Cloak of Flames/Cloak of Crystalline Waters are a lot more rantable...<br>
<br>
CSM/LDA has always been a integrity oriented group.  They are one of the longest running small alliances I know of that wouldn't work without communication and integrity.  I'd question your motives as to why this &quot;belt&quot; was such a big deal to you a lot more then their integrity for looting it.<br>
<br>
Grats Rasza on 65 and the RBB.  It's about time!<br>
