I am Shynne Erotas, First Officer of Clan Silvermoon. I have been with CSM since October 2002. One of the main reasons I joined the CSM/LaDA alliance is because of their fair play, kind consideration of others and willingness to help out no matter what guild you are from. The people in these guilds are without a doubt some of the most honorable and honest you will find. I have had the pleasure of raiding and grouping with many, if not all of these people at one time or another and you will not find a greater bunch. <br>
